default
default&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0; 
defaultEach Region
default&#xa0;
default(South, Central and North England) has Public Sector Teams developing local partnerships.
default&#xa0;
default
default&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0; 
defaultThis work is supported by a Bid Writing and Resources Team. 
defaultIn 2012/13 the Public Sectors Team’s raised £18 million and secured significant funds through Local Government Procurement. 
