default2.1
default 
defaultIn general Local Authorities have developed long term relationships with The Prince’s Trust, even when significant changes have taken place. It is incumbent upon both parties to ensure that relationships can withstand organisational change.
default&#xa0;default2.2
default 
defaultIn the current climate, where there are still significant changes taking place within Local Authorities, key personnel can, and have, often changed, resulting in new relationships having to be formed and historic events re-visited to ensure clarity. Do Local Authorities use any form of partnership Customer Relationship Management that they update on a regular basis?
