defaultMulti Local Authority Frameworks would increase efficiencies for Local Authorities and suppliers for example Manchester City Council Troubled Families Supplier Framework can be used by 22 North West Local Authorities. 
default default&#xa0;default3.2
default 
defaultThis is beginning to happen in some areas, for example in South Yorkshire, West Yorkshire and the North East Local Authorities worked together to bid for 2013-15 ESF NEET funding. 
